'''玛格丽特·露丝·“玛吉”·吉伦哈尔'''（{{lang-en|Margaret Ruth "Maggie" Gyllenhaal}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://madame.lefigaro.fr/celebrites/maggie-gyllenhaal-250609-120089 |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal |last=Stérin |first=Gabrielle |date=2009-06-25 |work=Le Figaro |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-09-19 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130919175029/http://madame.lefigaro.fr/celebrites/maggie-gyllenhaal-250609-120089 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，{{bd|1977年|11月16日}}）是美国女演员和导演。做为{{le|吉伦哈尔家族|Gyllenhaal family}}的一员，她是导演[[史蒂芬·吉伦哈尔|史蒂芬·吉伦哈尔]]和[[剧作家|剧作家]][[妮奥美·芳娜·吉伦哈尔|妮奥美·芳娜·吉伦哈尔]]之女，也是男演员[[杰克·吉林哈尔|杰克·吉林哈尔]]的姐姐。

她首次亮相大银幕就是在父亲的电影中，之后在[[2001年电影|2001年]]的[[独立电影|独立制作]][[邪典电影|邪典电影]]《[[死亡幻觉|死亡幻觉]]》中出演配角而开始获得认同。[[2002年电影|2002年]]的[[虐恋|虐恋]][[爱情片|爱情片]]《[[秘书_(电影)|秘书]]》是吉伦哈尔取得突破的作品，她因此赢得了评价界的好评和[[金球奖|金球奖]]提名。

吉伦哈尔出演过多种类型的电影，包括[[2006年电影|2006年]]为她再次赢得金球奖提名的《[[雪莉宝贝|雪莉宝贝]]》，爱情[[喜剧片|喜剧片]]《[[相信男人|相信男人]]》，还有多部大成本电影，如《[[世贸中心_(电影)|世贸中心]]》和《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》。她还因在[[2009年电影|2009年]]的音乐剧情片《[[疯狂的心|疯狂的心]]》中出演而获得[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|奥斯卡最佳女配角奖]]提名。此外，吉伦哈尔还出演过[[舞台剧|舞台剧]]和多部[[电视电影|电视电影]]，如2000年的《[[偷心_(舞台剧)|偷心]]》和2004年的《[[搜身_(电影)|搜身]]》。

吉伦哈尔自2002年起与[[彼得·萨斯加德|彼得·萨斯加德]]交往，两人于2006年[[订婚|订婚]]，他们的女儿雷蒙娜也在2006年10月3日出世。2009年5月2日，两人在[[意大利|意大利]]成婚，他们的次女格洛丽亚·雷于2012年4月9日降生。吉伦哈尔是位政治上很积极的[[民主党_(美国)|民主党人]]，并且与双亲和弟弟一样都是[[美国公民自由联盟|美国公民自由联盟]]的支持者。2003年美国对[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]开战前，她参与了[[全球反对对伊战争大游行|反战游行]]。她还积极参与[[人权|人权]]、[[公民自由|公民自由]]、消除贫困和[[父母触发|父母触发]]事务。

== 早年生活 ==
吉伦哈尔生于[[纽约|纽约]]，是电影导演史蒂芬·吉伦哈尔和电影[[制片人|制片人]]兼剧作家妮奥美·芳娜·吉伦哈尔的女儿，母亲的[[女性人名|娘家姓]]是阿克斯（{{lang|en|Achs}}）<ref name="Maggie Gyllenhaal In The Con">{{cite news |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140207073714/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/maggie-gyllenhaal-in-the-con/ |deadurl=no |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/maggie-gyllenhaal-in-the-con/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal In The Con |archivedate= 2014-02-07 |accessdate=2014-02-26 |date=2006-08-30 |publisher=CBS News |work=The Early Show}}</ref>。她的弟弟杰克·吉伦哈尔也是一位演员，父亲有[[瑞典|瑞典]]和[[英国|英国]]血统，是瑞典[[贵族|贵族]]吉伦哈尔家族成员<ref name="ReferenceA">Stated on ''Finding Your Roots with Henry Louis Gates, Jr.'', PBS, 2012-04-22</ref>。高祖父安德斯·伦纳德·吉伦哈尔（{{lang|en|Anders Leonard Gyllenhaal}}）是她的最后一位瑞典本土祖先，后者又是瑞典军官兼[[昆虫学|昆虫学家]]伦纳德·吉伦哈尔（{{lang|en|Leonard Gyllenhaal}}）的后人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.talktalk.co.uk/entertainment/film/biography/artist/jake-gyllenhaal/biography/161 |title=Jake Gyllenhaal Biography |publisher=Tiscali |last=Wills |first=Dominic |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-10-22 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022012000/http://www.talktalk.co.uk/entertainment/film/biography/artist/jake-gyllenhaal/biography/161 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。母亲生于纽约市，来自从[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]和[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]移民的[[犹太人|犹太人]]家庭。母亲之前曾与[[历史学家|历史学家]]，[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]历史学[[教授|教授]][[埃里克·方纳|埃里克·方纳]]（{{lang|en|Eric Foner}}）结过婚<ref name="ReferenceA" /><ref>{{cite web |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal talks unions, education and motherhood |author=Howard Gensler |url=http://articles.philly.com/2012-09-28/news/34149452_1_anti-union-bias-teachers-union-top-charter-school |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022192611/http://articles.philly.com/2012-09-28/news/34149452_1_anti-union-bias-teachers-union-top-charter-school |archivedate=2013-10-22 |date=2012-09-28 |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.columbiaspectator.com/2008/09/10/brinkley-fans-bring-their-love-facebook |title=Brinkley Fans Bring Their Love to Facebook |last=Ferro |first=Shane |date=2008-09-10 |work=Columbia Daily Spectator |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022140923/http://www.columbiaspectator.com/2008/09/10/brinkley-fans-bring-their-love-facebook |archivedate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="education">{{cite news |first=Gaby |last=Wood |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2006/sep/17/features.magazine |title=Stealing beauty |accessdate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no |date=2006-09-17 |work=The Guardian |publisher=''guardian.co.uk'' |location=London |archivedate=2014-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109150505/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2006/sep/17/features.magazine}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2011-09-12 |deadurl=yes |title=The indie queen: Maggie Gyllenhaal discusses her role as a sex-crazed ex-con |last=Hoggard |first=Liz |date=2007-07-26 |work=The Independent |accessdate=2011-09-12 |location=London |url= http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/the-indie-queen-maggie-gyllenhaal-discusses-her-role-as-a-sexcrazed-excon-458789.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110912060702/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/the-indie-queen-maggie-gyllenhaal-discusses-her-role-as-a-sexcrazed-excon-458789.html}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔曾表示自己“从文化上总地来说是在犹太环境中长大的”，不过她并没有进入[[希伯莱文学校|希伯莱文学校]]就读<ref>{{cite web |title=Q&A: Maggie Gyllenhaal on 'Hysteria' |url=http://blogs.forward.com/the-arty-semite/155670/q-and-a-maggie-gyllenhaal-on-hysteria/ |accessdate= 2014-02-26 |archivedate=2014-02-21 |deadurl=no |publisher=The Forward Association, Inc. |work=The Arty Semite |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221110852/http://blogs.forward.com/the-arty-semite/155670/q-and-a-maggie-gyllenhaal-on-hysteria/}}</ref>。她的父母于1977年[[结婚|结婚]]，2008年10月提出离婚<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-10-21 |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20233907,00.html |title=Jake and Maggie Gyllenhaal's Parents Call it Quits |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021090027/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20233907,00.html |last=Lee |first=Ken |date=2008-10-17 |work=People |accessdate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。玛吉·吉伦哈尔出生证明上的名字是玛戈里特（{{lang|en|Margolit}}），但她一直到2013年正式更名为玛吉（{{lang|en|Maggie}}）时才发现这点<ref>{{cite web |url=http://video.lycos.com.au/news/view/maggie-gyllenhaal-mom-forgot-my-name-311175/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal: Mom forgot my name |date=2013-07-29 |accessdate=2014-02-26 |publisher=Lycos, Inc. |archivedate=2013-10-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014173329/http://video.lycos.com.au/news/view/maggie-gyllenhaal-mom-forgot-my-name-311175/}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]长大，并进入[[哈佛西湖学校|哈佛西湖]]预科学校就读<ref name="education" />。1995年，她从哈佛西湖学校毕业后前往纽约就读哥伦比亚大学，学习文学和东方宗教专业<ref name="education" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/maggie-gyllenhaal-scones-and-sampm-590195.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal: Scones and S&M |last=O'Sullivan |first=Charlotte |date=2003-05-09 |work=The Independent |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216191438/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/maggie-gyllenhaal-scones-and-sampm-590195.html |archivedate=2013-12-16 |accessdate=2014-02-26 |location=London |deadurl=no}}</ref>，并于1999毕业，获得文学士学位<ref name="education" />。之后她进入[[伦敦|伦敦]][[皇家戏剧艺术学院|皇家戏剧艺术学院]]学习<ref name="multiple">{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131223044327/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/MULTIPLE-MAGGIES-2491261.php |url=http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/MULTIPLE-MAGGIES-2491261.php |title=Multiple Maggies |last=Hart |first=Hugh |date=2006-08-13 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，暑期在[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的一家餐馆打工做女招待<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/secretary-a-breakthrough-role/ |title=Secretary: A Breakthrough Role? |date=2002-10-15 |work=The Early Show |publisher=CBS News |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140207074638/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/secretary-a-breakthrough-role/ |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-02-07}}</ref>。

== 事业 ==
=== 早期作品 ===
吉伦哈尔最早在大银幕上亮相的作品——如[[1992年电影|1992年]]的电影处女作《水之乡》（{{lang|en|''Waterland''}}）、1993年的《[[危险的情人|危险的情人]]》（{{lang|en|''A Dangerous Woman''}}）和1998年的《王牌追杀令》（{{lang|en|''Homegrown''}}）——都是自己父亲执导的，其中后两部还有弟弟杰克出镜，两人扮演片中起陪衬作用的儿童角色<ref name="education" />。两姐弟还和母亲一起出现在两期意大利美食节目《莫尔托·马里奥》（{{lang|en|''Molto Mario''}}）中，该节目有在美国的[[美食频道_(美国)|美食频道]]播出<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2014-01-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140116200054/http://www.amateurgourmet.com/2006/05/marios_celebrit.html |url=http://www.amateurgourmet.com/2006/05/marios_celebrit.html |title=Mario's Celebrity Guests |last=Roberts |first=Adam |date=2006-05-23 |work=Amateur Gourmet |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。大学毕业后，她在《[[疯狂的塞西尔|疯狂的塞西尔]]》（{{lang|en|''Cecil B. Demented''}}）<ref>{{cite news |title=Cecil B. Demented |last=Zacharek |first=Stephanie |date=2000-08-11 |publisher=Salon.com |accessdate=2008-12-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=CECIL B. DEMENTED |publisher=Festival de Cannes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029212946/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/5207/year/2000.html |accessdate=2014-02-26 |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/5207/year/2000.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>和《[[与男孩同车|与男孩同车]]》（{{lang|en|''Riding in Cars with Boys''}}）等电影中出演配角<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0200027/fullcredits?ref_=tt_cl_sm#cast |title=Riding in Cars with Boys (2001) Full Cast & Crew |work=IMDb |publisher=Amazon |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-04-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414182739/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0200027/fullcredits#cast |deadurl=no }}</ref>，并因2001年的独立制作邪典电影《[[死亡幻觉|死亡幻觉]]》成名，该片由杰克·吉伦哈尔出演，她在片中饰演的角色正好也是杰克角色的姐姐<ref name="aftermath">{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/jul/07/2 |title=Looking for trouble |last=Cartner-Morley |first=Jess |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222101422/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/jul/07/2 |date=2007-07-02 |work=The Guardian |publisher=''guardian.co.uk'' |accessdate=2014-02-26 |location=London |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔的舞台剧处女作是[[派崔克·马柏|派崔克·马柏]]（{{lang|en|Patrick Marber}}）的《偷心》（{{lang|en|''Closer''}}），由伯克利话剧团制作<ref name="play">{{cite news |first=Ben |last=Brantley |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222164404/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/13/theater/theater-review-afghanistan-still-stirs-a-housewife.html |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/13/theater/theater-review-afghanistan-still-stirs-a-housewife.html |title=Theater Review; Afghanistan Still Stirs A Housewife |accessdate=2014-02-26 |date=2004-05-13 |work=The New York Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2014-02-08 |url=http://www.berkeleyrep.org/about/past.asp#tabbed-nav=1990s |title=Past Productions |work=Berkeley Repertory Theatre Official Site |accessdate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140208025435/http://www.berkeleyrep.org/about/past.asp#tabbed-nav=1990s}}</ref>，这次演出为她赢得了好评<ref name="production time" /><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222122846/http://www.laweekly.com/2000-11-23/stage/affairs-of-the-heartless/ |url=http://www.laweekly.com/2000-11-23/stage/affairs-of-the-heartless/ |title=Affairs of the Heartless |last=Morris |first=Steven Leigh |date=2000-11-23 |work=LA Weekly |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。制作于2000年5月开始，同年7月中旬结束<ref name="production time">{{cite news |archivedate=2012-06-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120621043511/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=%2Fexaminer%2Farchive%2F2000%2F05%2F25%2FSTYLE12203.dtl&type=performance |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/examiner/archive/2000/05/25/STYLE12203.dtl&type=performance |title=Seductio ad absurdum |last=Hurwitt |first=Robert |date=2000-05-25 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=2012-06-21 }}</ref>。她还出演了其他多部舞台剧，包括《[[暴风雨_(莎士比亚)|暴风雨]]》<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/27/theater/theaterspecial/27schi.html?pagewanted=print&position=&_r=0 |title=Ebon Moss-Bachrach |last=Schillinger |first=Liesl |date=2005-02-27 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226085206/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/27/theater/theaterspecial/27schi.html?pagewanted=print&position=&_r=0 |archivedate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref>、《[[安东尼和克娄帕特拉|安东尼和克娄帕特拉]]》（{{lang|en|''Antony and Cleopatra''}}）、《蝴蝶计划》（{{lang|en|''The Butterfly Project''}}）和《[[无处逃生|无处逃生]]》（{{lang|en|''No Exit''}}）<ref>{{cite news |title=Cecil B. Demented — Production Notes |date=2000-08 |work=Seattle Post-Intelligencer |accessdate=2008-11-04}}</ref>。

=== 2002至2005年 ===
