2002年的[[黑色幽默|黑色]]爱情片《秘书》（{{lang|en|''Secretary''}}）给吉伦哈尔带来了事业上的突破，影片讲述的是两人互相为对方实现{{lang|en|[[BDSM|BDSM]]}}生活方式的故事<ref name="ny times" />。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》影评人斯蒂芬·霍尔登（{{lang|en|Stephen Holden}}）指出：“玛吉·吉伦哈尔给李一角注入了内敛、精致而甜蜜的特性，她应该会成为明星。”<ref name="ny times">{{cite news |quote=The role of Lee, which Maggie Gyllenhaal imbues with a restrained comic delicacy and sweetness, should make her a star. |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/20/movies/20SECR.html |title=Film Review: An Office Disciplinarian Gets His Way in the End |last=Holden |first=Stephen |date=2002-09-20 |work=The New York Times |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100221080629/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/20/movies/20SECR.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2010-02-21 |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的米克·拉萨尔（{{lang|en|Mick LaSalle}}）写道：“玛吉·吉伦哈尔饰演的这个有自我毁灭倾向的秘书高深莫测，而且时时会激发出观众的同情。”<ref>{{cite news |quote=Maggie Gyllenhaal, as the self-destructive secretary, is enigmatic and, at moments, sympathetic. |url=http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/FILM-CLIPS-Also-opening-today-2766711.php |title='Secretary' |last=LaSalle |first=Mick |date=2002-09-27 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-12-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223051216/http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/FILM-CLIPS-Also-opening-today-2766711.php |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片获得了总体较为正面的评价<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/secretary |title=Secretary (2002): Reviews |publisher=Metacritic |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130918151621/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/secretary |accessdate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-09-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secretary/ |title=Secretary (2002) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828145039/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secretary/ |publisher=Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-08-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，吉伦哈尔的表演为她赢得了[[国家评论协会|国家评论协会]]的女演员最具突破性演出奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nationalboardofreview.org/award-years/2002/ |title=National Board of Review of Motion Pictures – Awards for 2002 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |work=National Board of Review of Motion Pictures Official Website |archive-date=2017-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107190644/http://www.nationalboardofreview.org/award-years/2002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和第一个金球奖提名<ref name="hfpa">{{cite web |archivedate=2014-02-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220084233/http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=%2Fmember%2F29619 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=/member/29619 |title=Browse Results - Maggie Gyllenhaal |accessdate=2014-02-26 |work=Golden Globes Official Website }}</ref>以及[[独立精神奖|独立精神奖]]提名<ref>{{cite journal |first=Addison |last=Pate |title=Independent film nominees announced |date=2002-12-11 |work=Whittier Daily News}}</ref>。《秘书》也是吉伦哈尔第一次在电影中正面全裸<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2011-06-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110624113856/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article2098029.ece |url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article2098029.ece |title=A star and ‘momma-lion’|last=Bone |first=James |date=2007-07-19 |work=The Times |accessdate=2011-06-24 |location=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20211226,00.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Hates Fiancé's Love Scenes |last=Jessen |first=Monique |date=2008-07-09 |work=People |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918232921/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20211226,00.html |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，虽然对其剧本留下了深刻印象，但她起初对出演存有顾虑，觉得其中会传达出一种反女权主义思潮，但经过与导演史蒂芬·西恩博格（{{lang|en|Steven Shainberg}}）细致探讨后最终同意加盟<ref>{{cite news |first=Tom |last=Dawson |archivedate=2013-09-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130919204603/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2003/05/06/maggie_gyllenhaal_secretary_interview.shtml |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2003/05/06/maggie_gyllenhaal_secretary_interview.shtml |title=Secretary |accessdate=2014-02-26 |date=2003-05-06 |publisher=BBC |work=BBC Films}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔表示西恩博格并没有利用她，不过影片开拍时自己的确感觉有些害怕。她也对导演给予了高度评价，称要是换一个人来执导，哪怕在能力上只比西恩博格差一点点，这也会变成一部非常怪异的电影<ref name="aftermath" />。从此以后，她对探讨这个角色抱有戒心，表示不希望自己的工作渗透到生活中<ref name="aftermath" />。

接下来，她在[[2002年电影|2002年]]的喜剧[[剧情片|剧情片]]《[[改编剧本|改编剧本]]》中出演一个配角，该片讲述了剧作家[[查理·卡夫曼|查理·卡夫曼]]努力试图将一本名为《兰花窃贼》（{{lang|en|''The Orchid Thief''}}）的小说改编成电影的故事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2002/12/06/movies/06ADAP.html |title=Film Review; Forever Obsessing About Obsession |last=Scott |first=A.O. |date=2002-12-06 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111201024721/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/12/06/movies/06ADAP.html |archivedate = 2011-12-01 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。接下来她与[[山姆·洛克威尔|山姆·洛克威尔]]、[[德鲁·巴里摩尔|德鲁·巴里摩尔]]、[[乔治·克鲁尼|乔治·克鲁尼]]和[[朱莉娅·罗伯茨|朱莉娅·罗伯茨]]合作出演了《[[危险思想的自白|危险思想的自白]]》（{{lang|en|''Confessions of a Dangerous Mind''}}）<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-09-19 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130919222853/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2003/02/14/confessions_of_a_dangerous_mind_2003_review.shtml |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2003/02/14/confessions_of_a_dangerous_mind_2003_review.shtml |title=Confessions of a Dangerous Mind (2003) Review |last=Pierce |first=Nev |date=2003-03-16 |work=BBC Films |deadurl=no |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，该片的全球票房达到3300万美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=confessionsofadangerousmind.htm |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131228002536/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=confessionsofadangerousmind.htm |title=Confessions of a Dangerous Mind (2002) |accessdate=2014-02-26 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |archivedate=2013-12-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。同年她还在喜剧片《[[禁欲40天|禁欲40天]]》（{{lang|en|''40 Days and 40 Nights''}}）中出演了一个小角色<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1515123/maggie-gyllenhaal-licks-fear-romantic-comedy.jhtml |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Overcomes Her Fear Of Romantic Comedies |last=Meyers |first=Shelby |date=2005-11-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223045741/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1515123/maggie-gyllenhaal-licks-fear-romantic-comedy.jhtml |archivedate=2013-12-23 |deadurl=no |work=MTV Movie News |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。

2003年，她在朱莉娅·罗伯茨主演的《[[蒙娜丽莎的微笑|蒙娜丽莎的微笑]]》中出演吉赛尔·利维（{{lang|en|Giselle Levy}}）一角<ref name="People - Bio">{{cite web |first=Janet |last=Mock |url=http://www.people.com/people/maggie_gyllenhaal/biography |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Biography |accessdate=2014-02-26 |work=People |archivedate=2014-01-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140122215804/http://www.people.com/people/maggie_gyllenhaal/biography/}}</ref>。一次接受《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》[[采访|采访]]时，她透露自己之所以接演这个角色是希望“可以诠释一位对自己的[[性感|性感]]和[[美丽|美丽]]感到自信的女性”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3612432/Girl-on-top.html |title=Girl on top |last=Campion |first=Chris |date=2004-02-16 |work=The Daily Telegraph |accessdate=2014-02-26 |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917235614/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3612432/Girl-on-top.html |archivedate=2013-09-17 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。该片所获评价不佳<ref>{{cite web |title=Mona Lisa Smile (2003) |publisher= Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mona_lisa_smile/ |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105040625/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mona_lisa_smile/ |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-11-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-09-18 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130918134536/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mona-lisa-smile |deadurl=no |url= http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mona-lisa-smile |title=Mona Lisa Smile (2003): Review |date=2003-12-19 |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的马诺拉·达吉斯（{{lang|en|Manohla Dargis}}）批评影片“自鸣得意，原型毕露”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/cl-et-dargis19dec19,2,3006745.story |title='Mona Lisa Smile' |last=Dargis |first=Manohla |date=2003-12-19 |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2010-04-18 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100418060602/http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/cl-et-dargis19dec19,2,3006745.story |archivedate = 2010-04-18 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔接下来出演了两部独立电影。一部是2003年的《[[育婴房|育婴房]]》（{{lang|en|''Casa de los Babys''}}），讲述了六位美国女性迫不及待地想要在某个[[南美洲|南美洲]]国家领养孩子的故事<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-01-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140116183113/http://www.villagevoice.com/2003-09-16/film/frustrated-mothers-to-be-flounder-in-saylesian-purgatory/ |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2003-09-16/film/frustrated-mothers-to-be-flounder-in-saylesian-purgatory/ |title=Frustrated Mothers-to-Be Flounder in Saylesian Purgatory |last=Ng |first=David |date=2003-09-16 |work=The Village Voice |accessdate=2014-02-26 |page=1}}</ref>；另一部是与[[约翰·C·赖利|约翰·C·赖利]]和[[迭戈·鲁纳|迭戈·鲁纳]]合作出演的[[2004年电影|2004年电影]]《[[罪犯_(电影)|罪犯]]》（{{lang|en|''Criminal''}}），是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]影片《[[九个皇后|九个皇后]]》（{{lang|en|''Nine Queens''}}）的翻拍<ref name="nine" />，她饰演的是一位诚实的酒店经理，被迫帮自己吸毒的哥哥去勾引他的受害人<ref name="nine">{{cite news |url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/Film/Modern-Maggie/2005/04/28/1114635687879.html |title=Thoroughly modern Maggie |last=Bunbury |first=Stephanie |date=2005-04-28 |work=The Age |accessdate=2014-02-26 |location=Melbourne |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917212333/http://www.theage.com.au/news/Film/Modern-Maggie/2005/04/28/1114635687879.html |archivedate=2013-09-17 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。到了2004年，吉伦哈尔获邀加入[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,662249,00.html |title=The Academy announces Oscar membership invitations |last=Young |first=Josh |date=2004-07-16 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208042123/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,662249,00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-12-08}}</ref>。这年她还主演了{{lang|en|[[HBO|HBO]]}}的电视电影《搜身》（{{lang|en|''Strip Search''}}），饰演一位在中国求学的美国学生，遭到涉嫌[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]的指控<ref>{{cite news |first=Corey |last=Moss |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131223051300/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485942/gyllenhaal-sarsgaard-avoid-gigli-problem.jhtml |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485942/gyllenhaal-sarsgaard-avoid-gigli-problem.jhtml |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal, Peter Sarsgaard Avoid Potential 'Gigli' Problem |accessdate=2014-02-26 |date=2010-03-24 |publisher=MTV News |archivedate=2013-12-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2004年，吉伦哈尔还回归舞台，参加了[[托尼·库什纳|托尼·库什纳]]的洛杉矶版《鸿勃笛/喀布尔》（{{lang|en|''Homebody/ Kabul''}}）演出，她诠释的是鸿勃笛的女儿普丽西拉（{{lang|en|Priscilla}}），出场大部分时间里都是在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[喀布尔|喀布尔]]寻找自己的[[母亲|母亲]]。库什纳是看到吉伦哈尔在《偷心》中的演出后决定让她出演这个角色<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/09/theater/theater-homebody-comes-home-a-mere-17-drafts-later.html |title='Homebody' Comes Home, A Mere 17 Drafts Later |last=Dominus |first=Susan |date=2004-05-09 |work=The New York Times |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222163916/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/09/theater/theater-homebody-comes-home-a-mere-17-drafts-later.html |archivedate=2013-12-22 |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的本·布兰特利（{{lang|en|Ben Brantley}}）称赞她的表演给角色和剧目标题之间建立起了不可或缺的桥梁<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130918103956/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/13/theater/theater-review-afghanistan-still-stirs-a-housewife.html?pagewanted=2 |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/13/theater/theater-review-afghanistan-still-stirs-a-housewife.html?pagewanted=2 |title=Theater Review; Afghanistan Still Stirs A Housewife |last=Brantley |first=Ben |date=2004-05-13 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-02-26 |page=2}}</ref>。《[[纽约观察家|纽约观察家]]》（{{lang|en|''The New York Observer''}}）的约翰·海尔佩恩（{{lang|en|John Heilpern}}）也认为吉伦哈尔的表演“让人信服”<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no |url=http://observer.com/2004/05/homebodykabul-returns-to-a-world-that-lost-its-mind/ |title=Homebody/Kabul Returns To a World That Lost Its Mind |last=Heilpern |first=John |date=2004-05-30 |work=The New York Observer |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226125222/http://observer.com/2004/05/homebodykabul-returns-to-a-world-that-lost-its-mind/}}</ref>。2004年至2005年，她入选了《[[美信|美信]]》[[杂志|杂志]]评选的“百大性感女性名单”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-04-09-maxim-100_x.htm |title='Maxim' Top 100 Hot list 2004 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224163406/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-04-09-maxim-100_x.htm |date=2004-04-09 |work=USA Today |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-12-24 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-03-23-fhm-sexiest-women_x.htm |title=Jolie sizzles atop 'FHM' sexiest list |last=Soriano |first=César G. |date=2005-03-23 |work=USA Today |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-12-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219150113/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-03-23-fhm-sexiest-women_x.htm |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔出演的下一部电影是2005年的喜剧剧情片《[[幸福结局_(电影)|幸福结局]]》（{{lang|en|''Happy Endings''}}），她扮演的是一位歌手，试图勾引一位年轻的[[同性恋|同性恋]][[音乐家|音乐家]]（[[杰森·雷特|杰森·雷特]]）和他有钱的父亲（[[汤姆·阿诺德|汤姆·阿诺德]]）。她为影片亲自献唱，录制了多首歌曲<ref name="People - Bio" /><ref name="live">{{cite news |author=Associated Press |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131224153938/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-07-29-gyllenhaal_x.htm?POE=LIFISVA |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-07-29-gyllenhaal_x.htm?POE=LIFISVA |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal insists on live singing |date=2005-07-29 |work=USA Today |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-12-24 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，称这是自己演过“最强悍，最可怕的”角色，还补充表示自己在银幕上献唱时比表演更加自然<ref name="live" />。影片所获评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/happy_endings/ |title=Happy Endings (2005) |publisher=Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-09-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130902015653/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/happy_endings/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/happy-endings |title=Happy Endings |publisher=CBS |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-06-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130625153342/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/happy-endings}}</ref>，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的丽莎·施瓦兹包恩（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）认为吉伦哈尔所表现出的美妙且自然慵懒的性感有些做作<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1082764,00.html |title=Happy Endings Review |last=Schwarzbaum |first=Lisa |date=2005-07-13 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-12-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131208053801/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1082764,00.html}}</ref>。

