除《幸福结局》外，她还出演了多部2006年的电影，如《相信男人》、《[[奇幻人生|奇幻人生]]》、《[[怪兽屋|怪兽屋]]》、《世贸中心》和《雪莉宝贝》。其中《相信男人》由吉伦哈尔和[[朱丽安·摩尔|朱丽安·摩尔]]、[[大卫·杜楚尼|大卫·杜楚尼]]以及[[比利·克鲁德普|比利·克鲁德普]]（{{lang|en|Billy Crudup}}）共同出演，她饰演与克鲁德普的角色托比（{{lang|en|Tobey}}）交往了七年的伊莱恩（{{lang|en|Elaine}}），开始感觉是时候安顿下来成家了<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-10-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121024071635/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2006/08/18/dont_trust_this_insufferable_man/ |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2006/08/18/dont_trust_this_insufferable_man/ |title='Trust the Man' is an insufferable experience |last=Morris |first=Wesley |date=2006-08-18 |work=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-03-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120308211803/http://chicago.metromix.com/movies/review/movie-review-trust-the/167816/content |url=http://chicago.metromix.com/movies/review/movie-review-trust-the/167816/content |title=Movie review: 'Trust the Man' |last=Reaves |first=Jessica |date=2007-09-04 |work=Chicago Tribune |accessdate=2012-03-08}}</ref>。这部电影无论是商业还是评论两方面都不成功<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/trust-the-man |title=Trust the Man (2006): Reviews |date=2006-08-18 |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918142945/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/trust-the-man}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trust_the_man/ |title=Trust the Man |date=2006-08-18 |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115014809/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trust_the_man |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-11-15 |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，不过《[[首映_(杂志)|首映]]》杂志的伊森·阿尔特（{{lang|en|Ethan Alter}}）觉得吉伦哈尔和克鲁德普的表演远比其他演员要轻松自然，他认为这“可能是因为他们都已经多次出演过这类角色”<ref>{{cite journal |title=Premiere — Trust the Man |last=Alter |first=Ethan |date=2006-08-17 |work=Premiere}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔在《奇幻人生》中饰演的是[[威尔·法瑞尔|威尔·法瑞尔]]角色的心上人<ref>{{cite news |first=A.O. |last=Scott |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/10/movies/10fict.html?_r=0 |title=Stranger Than Fiction — Hearing Voices? It's Just Somebody’s Imagination |accessdate=2014-02-26 |date=2006-11-10 |work=The New York Times |archivedate=2011-08-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812234347/http://movies.nytimes.com/2006/11/10/movies/10fict.html |deadurl=no}}</ref>，演出获得了影评人的好评，[[福斯新闻频道|福克斯新闻]]的麦克·斯特拉卡（{{lang|en|Mike Straka}}）称赞这是她在电影中最性感的一次演出，并且无疑可以让她获得更多出演一流制作影片的机会，而不再需要接演独立制作<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-01-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140116181636/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/11/10/maggie-gyllenhaal-awesome-in-stranger-than-fiction/ |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/11/10/maggie-gyllenhaal-awesome-in-stranger-than-fiction/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Awesome in 'Stranger Than Fiction' |last=Straka |first=Mike |date=2006-11-10 |publisher=Fox News |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔在[[计算机动画|计算机动画]][[恐怖电影|恐怖电影]]《怪兽屋》中为伊丽莎白（{{lang|en|Elizabeth}}）[[配音|配音]]<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-01-16 |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2006/07/21/monster_house_is_built_just_for_kids/ |title=Built just for kids |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116194218/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2006/07/21/monster_house_is_built_just_for_kids |deadurl=no |last=Burr |first=Ty |date=2006-07-21 |work=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，还在[[奥利佛·斯通|奥利佛·斯通]]执导，以[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]为背景的大制作影片《世贸中心》中诠释港务局官员[[威尔·吉米诺|威尔·吉米诺]]（{{lang|en|Will Jimeno}}）的妻子艾莉森·吉米诺（{{lang|en|Allison Jimeno}}）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.seattlepi.com/ae/movies/article/Stone-delivers-a-dignified-and-intelligent-9-11-1211112.php |title=Stone delivers a dignified and intelligent 9/11 film |last=Arnold |first=William |date=2006-08-09 |work=Seattle Post-Intelligencer |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222052955/http://www.seattlepi.com/ae/movies/article/Stone-delivers-a-dignified-and-intelligent-9-11-1211112.php |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。她表示《世贸中心》是所接演电影中最让自己感到愉快的其中一部<ref name="aftermath" />，该片获得了商业的评论上的成功，全球票房超过1.62亿[[美元|美元]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/world-trade-center |title=World Trade Center (2006): Reviews |date=2006-08-09 |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918133010/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/world-trade-center}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=wtc.htm |title=World Trade Center (2006) |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107211245/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=wtc.htm |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-01-07 |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=World Trade Center (2006) |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/world_trade_center/ |publisher=Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002060602/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/world_trade_center/ |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-10-02}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔在《雪莉宝贝》中出演一位年轻但[[吸毒|吸毒]]成瘾的窃贼，出狱后试图重整旗鼓，希望能获得女儿的谅解。她在为电影作宣传期间表示，扮演这样一个矛盾、天真而痛苦的角色让她也感觉到了那种痛苦<ref>{{cite news |archivedate= 2014-02-07 |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/maggie-gyllenhaal-mom-and-movie-star/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal: Mom And Movie Star |date=2006-09-01 |work=The Early Show |publisher=CBS News |accessdate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140207073734/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/maggie-gyllenhaal-mom-and-movie-star/}}</ref>。她在片中的表演赢得了良好的评价，[[美联社|美联社]]的大卫·格尔曼（{{lang|en|David Germain}}）称“吉伦哈尔如此深刻和丰富地人性化了这个角色……雪莉即便是在最黑暗、最脆弱的时刻也能引发（观众的）共鸣”<ref>{{cite journal |first=David |last=Germain |title=Gyllenhaal saves slim story in 'Sherrybaby' |date=2006-09-17 |work=Record-Journal |agency=Associated Press |page=F03}}</ref>；《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志的丹尼斯·哈维（{{lang|en|Dennis Harvey}}）称赞她的表演“混然天成”<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2011-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110815001121/http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_review/VE1117929318.html?nav=reviews07&categoryid=2352&cs=1&p=0 |url=http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_review/VE1117929318.html?nav=reviews07&categoryid=2352&cs=1&p=0 |title=Review of Sherrybaby |last=Harvey |first=Dennis |date=2006-01-22 |work=Variety |accessdate=2011-08-15}}</ref>，吉伦哈尔也因此再度获得金球奖提名<ref name="hfpa" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/03/16/AR2007031600522.html |title=For 'SherryBaby,' a Lingering Power |last=Hornaday |first=Ann |date=2007-03-16 |work=The Washington Post |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archive-date=2018-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025145926/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/03/16/AR2007031600522.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在2006年[[斯德哥尔摩电影节|斯德哥尔摩电影节]]上赢得最佳女演员奖<ref>{{cite news |author=Associated Press |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/11/27/AR2006112700301.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Wins Stockholm Honor |date=2006-11-27 |work=The Washington Post |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archive-date=2018-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025150014/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/11/27/AR2006112700301.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
