接下来，吉伦哈尔出演了[[2008年电影|2008年]]的《黑暗騎士》，该片是[[2005年电影|2005年电影]]《[[蝙蝠侠：侠影之谜|蝙蝠侠：侠影之谜]]》的[[续集|续集]]，她取代[[凯蒂·霍尔姆斯|凯蒂·霍尔姆斯]]饰演[[检察官|助理地区检察官]]蕾切尔·道斯（{{lang|en|Rachel Dawes}}）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2007/more/news/gyllenhaal-joining-batman-sequel-1117960782/ |title=Gyllenhaal joining Batman sequel |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |date=2007-03-08 |work=Variety |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226153303/http://variety.com/2007/more/news/gyllenhaal-joining-batman-sequel-1117960782/ |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Nancy |last=Ayala |archivedate=2013-10-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004140612/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=5398125&page=1 |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=5398125&page=1 |title='Dark Knight' Gets New Leading Lady |accessdate=2014-02-26 |date=2008-07-18 |publisher=ABC News}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔承认自己的角色在一定程度上属于老套的“[[落难女子|落难女子]]”类型，但她也表示，导演[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]已经设法令这个角色更加饱满，所以“蕾切尔的确清楚地知道对于自己来说最重要的是什么，她也不愿意在道德上作出妥协”，与她过去诠释的许多矛盾角色相比，这是“一次不错的改变”<ref>{{cite news |first=Andrew |last=Williams |archivedate=2014-02-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140207083059/http://metro.co.uk/2008/01/06/gyllenhaal-talks-sexy-underwear-370602/ |url=http://metro.co.uk/2008/01/06/gyllenhaal-talks-sexy-underwear-370602/ |title=Gyllenhaal Talks Sexy Underwear |work=Metro |date=2008-01-06 |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。《黑暗騎士》无论是在商业还是评价上都大获成功<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_knight/ |title=The Dark Knight (2008) |publisher=Flixster |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224211913/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_knight/ |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2014-02-24 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Dark Knight |url= http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-knight |publisher=CBS |work=metacritic |accessdate=2014-02-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209142618/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-knight |archivedate= 2014-02-09}}</ref>，创下了[[北美|北美]]上映首周的[[票房|票房]]新纪录，全球进账超过10亿美元<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140221104243/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=darkknight.htm |deadurl=no |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=darkknight.htm |title=The Dark Knight (2008) |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，如果不考虑[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]因素，截止2014年2月止，这个成绩仍然可以在历史上所有的电影中排到第17位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2014-02-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221101228/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/}}</ref>，也是吉伦哈尔出演过的电影中商业上最成功的。{{lang|en|[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]}}网站的斯蒂芬妮·扎克拉克（{{lang|en|Stephanie Zacharek}}）形容吉伦哈尔的角色是“穿着[[芭芭拉·斯坦威克|斯坦威克]]风格斜裁礼服的一块坚强的小糖饼”，并表示“当她出现在银幕上时，整部电影给人的感觉也更灵巧、更柔顺”<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2011-08-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110805225206/http://www.salon.com/entertainment/movies/review/2008/07/17/dark_knight/ |url=http://www.salon.com/entertainment/movies/review/2008/07/17/dark_knight/ |title=The Dark Knight |last=Zacharek |first=Stephanie |date=2008-07-17 |publisher=Salon.com |accessdate=2011-08-05}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站影评人托德·吉尔克里斯特（{{lang|en|Todd Gilchrist}}）写道：“吉伦哈尔给蕾切尔·道斯增加了真正的深度和能量”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/06/30/the-dark-knight-review?page=2 |title=IGN: The Dark Knight Review |last=Gilchrist |first=Todd |date=2008-06-30 |publisher=IGN Movies |page=2 |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2012-11-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105052650/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/06/30/the-dark-knight-review?page=2 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2009年，吉伦哈尔在经典舞台公司制作的[[外百老汇|外百老汇]]版[[安东·帕夫洛维奇·契诃夫|安东·帕夫洛维奇·契诃夫]]舞台剧《[[万尼亚舅舅|万尼亚舅舅]]》（{{lang|en|''Uncle Vanya''}}）中出演叶莲娜（{{lang|en|Yelena}}）一角<ref name="uncle">{{cite news |archivedate=2011-12-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111229233005/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/08/theater/08itzk.html |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/08/theater/08itzk.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |title=Together Off Broadway and Elsewhere |last=Itzkoff |first=Dave |date=2009-02-04 |work=The New York Times |page=1 |accessdate=2014-02-26 }}</ref><ref name="vanya">{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222184423/http://variety.com/2008/legit/news/gyllenhaal-sarsgaard-join-vanya-1117997230/ |url=http://variety.com/2008/legit/news/gyllenhaal-sarsgaard-join-vanya-1117997230/ |title=Gyllenhaal, Sarsgaard join 'Vanya' |last=Cox |first=Gordon |date=2008-12-11 |work=Variety |accessdate=2014-02-26}}</ref>，参加演出的还包括彼得·萨斯加德、[[麦米·古默|麦米·古默]]（{{lang|en|Mamie Gummer}}）、[[丹尼斯·欧哈拉|丹尼斯·欧哈拉]]（{{lang|en|Denis O'Hare}}）和乔治·莫法根（{{lang|en|George Morfogen}}）<ref name="uncle" /><ref name="vanya" />。这一版本由[[奥斯汀·潘德尔顿|奥斯汀·潘德尔顿]]（{{lang|en|Austin Pendleton}}）导演，只进行了限量放映，1月17日开始预演，3月1日结束演出<ref name="uncle" /><ref name="vanya" />。[[纽约每日新闻|纽约《每日新闻》]]的乔·迪兹米阿诺维奇（{{lang|en|Joe Dziemianowicz}}）对吉伦哈尔的表现评价一般，觉得她的表演单调、呆板，有太多《雪莉宝贝》的影子<ref>{{cite news |quote=Gyllenhaal, who was so dynamic as a druggie in the film ''Sherrybaby'', plays Yelena with a slow-mo saunter and monotonous pasted-on smile that makes it seem as if she's been in Sherry's stash. |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222173159/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/starry-chekhov-revival-uncle-vanya-clueless-article-1.393207 |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/starry-chekhov-revival-uncle-vanya-clueless-article-1.393207 |title=Starry Chekhov revival is 'Uncle Vanya' is 'Clueless' |last=Dziemianowicz |first=Joe |date=2009-02-13 |work=Daily News (New York) |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>。不过，《[[哈特福德新闻报|哈特福德新闻报]]》（{{lang|en|''Hartford Courant''}}）的马尔科姆·约翰逊（{{lang|en|Malcolm Johnson}}）给出了正面评价，称她的角色表现最终像花朵般盛开<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.courant.com/2009-02-13/news/vanyarev.art.art_1_uncle-vanya-estate-mamie-gummer |title=Chehov's 'Uncle Vanya" In Fine Revival |last=Johnson |first=Malcolm |date=2009-02-13 |work=The Hartford Courant |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208211049/http://articles.courant.com/2009-02-13/news/vanyarev.art.art_1_uncle-vanya-estate-mamie-gummer |archivedate=2013-12-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔与男演员[[约翰·卡拉辛斯基|约翰·卡拉辛斯基]]合作出演了导演[[萨姆·门德斯|萨姆·门德斯]]的喜剧片《[[为子搬迁|为子搬迁]]》（{{lang|en|''Away We Go''}}），该片于[[2009年电影|2009年]]上映，她饰演一位放荡不羁的大学教授，是卡拉辛斯基角色的老朋友<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2008/film/news/mendes-swaps-in-maggie-gyllenhaal-1117984967/ |title=Mendes swaps in Maggie Gyllenhaal |last=Siegel |first=Tatiana |date=2008-05-31 |work=Variety |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-12-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222185617/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/mendes-swaps-in-maggie-gyllenhaal-1117984967/ |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20197433,00.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130617072239/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20197433,00.html |title=Gyllenhaal Replaces Collette for Mendes |date=2008-05-31 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-06-17 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片所获评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/away-we-go |title=Away We Go (2009): Reviews |date=2009-06-05 |publisher=CBS |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918160241/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/away-we-go |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/away_we_go/ |title=Away We Go (2009) |publisher=Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-03-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130318221143/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/away_we_go/}}</ref>，《娱乐周刊》的欧文·格雷伯曼（{{lang|en|Owen Gleiberman}}）形容吉伦哈尔角色的次要情节有些“喧宾夺主”<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131208045248/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20282749,00.html |archivedate=2013-12-08 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20282749,00.html |title=Away We Go (2009): Reviews |last=Gleiberman |first=Owen |date=2009-06-05 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。不过《纽约时报》的{{lang|en|A·O}}·斯科特（{{lang|en|A. O. Scott}}）称赞她与另一位女演员[[艾莉森·珍妮|艾莉森·珍妮]]（{{lang|en|Allison Janney}}）的表演“都很有趣”<ref name="proud">{{cite news |archivedate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227060527/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/05/movies/05away.html?_r=0 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/05/movies/05away.html?_r=0 |title=Away We Go — Practicing Virtue, and Proud of It |last=Scott |first=A.O. |date=2009-06-05 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>，认为吉伦哈尔在片中有关“海马社区”[[性别角色|性别角色]]的台词是剧本中最讽刺的段落<ref name="proud" />。她的下一部作品是音乐剧情片《疯狂的心》，扮演[[记者|记者]]让·克拉多克（{{lang|en|Jean Craddock}}），与[[杰夫·布里吉斯|杰夫·布里吉斯]]演对手戏<ref name="parade">{{cite news |archivedate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140227064840/http://parade.condenast.com/31923/jeannewolf/maggie-gyllenhaal-on-motherhood-090707/ |url=http://parade.condenast.com/31923/jeannewolf/maggie-gyllenhaal-on-motherhood-090707/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal: All Moms Do 'The Best They Can' |last=Wolf |first=Jeanne |date=2009-07-07 |work=Parade |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>。该片获得了良好的评价<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crazy_heart/ |title=Crazy Heart (2009) |publisher=Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2014-02-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214122446/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crazy_heart/ |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/crazy-heart |title=Crazy Heart (2009): Reviews |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2009-12-16 |publisher=CBS |work=Metacritic |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918171249/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/crazy-heart |archivedate= 2013-09-18}}</ref>，《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》的彼得·特拉维斯（{{lang|en|Peter Travers}}）称赞吉伦哈尔饰演的克拉多克一角“风趣、感人而且重要”，把这个本来平淡无奇的角色演绎出了坚韧的智慧和情感<ref>{{cite news |first=Peter |last=Travers |title=Crazy Heart |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/crazy-heart-20091210 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131013173034/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/crazy-heart-20091210 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2009-12-10 |work=Rolling Stone |archivedate=2013-10-13}}</ref>。为此她赢得了自己的第一座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]提名：[[第82届奥斯卡金像奖|第82届奥斯卡金像奖]]女配角奖<ref>{{cite news |first=Alan |last=Duke |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/02/oscar.nominations/?hpt=Sbin |title='Avatar,' 'Hurt Locker' lead in Oscar nods |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2010-02-02 |publisher=CNN: Showbiz/Movies |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305100108/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/02/oscar.nominations/?hpt=Sbin |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Oscars2010">{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/82nd-winners.html |title=The 82nd Academy Awards (2010) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2013-10-16 |work=''Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences'' |publisher=AMPAS |archivedate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131224033929/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/82nd-winners.html}}</ref>。

=== 2010至2020年 ===
{{expand section}}
[[2010年电影|2010年]]，吉伦哈尔出演了《[[魔法保姆麦克菲2|魔法保姆麦克菲2]]》（{{lang|en|''Nanny McPhee and the Big Bang''}}），该片是2005年电影《[[魔法保姆麦克菲|魔法保姆麦克菲]]》（{{lang|en|''Nanny McPhee''}}）的续集<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208055747/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/04/14/maggie-gyllenha/ |deadurl=no |url=http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/04/14/maggie-gyllenha/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal joins 'Nanny McPhee' sequel |last=Vary |first=Adam B. |date=2009-04-14 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>，这个角色需要她以英国口音演出<ref>{{cite news |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal: interview for Away We Go |last=Lawrence |first=Will |date=2009-09-21 |work=The Daily Telegraph |accessdate=2014-02-27 |location=London |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130918040104/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/6188982/Maggie-Gyllenhaal-interview-for-Away-We-Go.html |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/6188982/Maggie-Gyllenhaal-interview-for-Away-We-Go.html}}</ref>。影片所获评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/nanny-mcphee-returns |title=Nanny McPhee Returns (2010): Reviews |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2010-08-20 |publisher=Metacritic |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918191651/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/nanny-mcphee-returns}}</ref>但总体偏向正面<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nanny_mcphee_returns/ |title=Nanny McPhee Returns (2010) |publisher=Flixster |work =Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-12-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131205113228/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nanny_mcphee_returns/}}</ref>，全球票房达到9325万美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=nannymcphee2.htm |title=Nanny McPhee Returns (2010) |accessdate=2014-02-27 |publisher=Amazon |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |archivedate=2013-10-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030170904/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=nannymcphee2.htm}}</ref>。她还在[[公共广播电视公司|公共电视网]]电视[[纪录片|纪录片]]系列节目《独立镜头》（{{lang|en|''Independent Lens''}}）中担任[[主持人|主持人]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pbs.org/independentlens/host.html |title=''Independent Lens'' Host |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130127030520/http://www.pbs.org/independentlens/about/host.html |archivedate=2013-01-27 |deadurl=no |publisher=Public Broadcasting Service}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔出演的下一部电影是[[2011年电影|2011年]]上映的《[[歇斯底里_(电影)|歇斯底里]]》（{{lang|en|''Hysteria''}}），这部独立制作影片取材于女性[[自慰|自慰]]震动棒的发明<ref>{{cite news |first=Catherine |last=Shoard |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222104911/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/aug/20/maggie-gyllenhaal-vibrator-love-story |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/aug/20/maggie-gyllenhaal-vibrator-love-story |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal hopes to hit the spot with vibrator love story |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2010-08-20 |work=The Guardian |location=London}}</ref>，所获评价一般<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hysteria_2012/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131221181313/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hysteria_2012/ |archivedate=2013-12-21 |deadurl=no |title=Hysteria (2011) |publisher=Flixster |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.metacritic.com/movie/hysteria |title=Hysteria |publisher=CBS |work=metacritic |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114155636/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/hysteria |archivedate=2012-11-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2011年2月，吉伦哈尔出演了另一部安东·帕夫洛维奇·契诃夫的舞台剧《[[三姐妹_(舞台剧)|三姐妹]]》，同样由奥斯汀·潘德尔顿导演，经典舞台公司制作，她扮演的是玛莎（{{lang|en|Masha}}）一角<ref>{{cite news |first=Scott |last=Brown |url=http://www.vulture.com/2011/02/stage_dive_the_three_sisters_a.html |title=Stage Dive: Sarsgaard and Gyllenhaal in ''Three Sisters'' as Robert Altman Cocktail Hour |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2011-02-03 |work=New York |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222085123/http://www.vulture.com/2011/02/stage_dive_the_three_sisters_a.html |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[彭博新闻社|彭博新闻社]]的杰里米·杰勒德（{{lang|en|Jeremy Gerard}}）将该剧概括为三姐妹“情场上的失意”以及“对返回[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的渴望”<ref>{{cite news |first=Jeremy |last=Gerard |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-04/gyllenhaal-falls-hard-for-husband-in-three-sisters-review.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Falls Hard for Husband in 'Three Sisters': Jeremy Gerard |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2011-02-03 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130917060927/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-04/gyllenhaal-falls-hard-for-husband-in-three-sisters-review.html |archivedate=2013-09-17 |deadurl=no |publisher=Bloomberg}}</ref>。节目于1月12日开始预演，并限量上演至3月6日<ref>{{cite news |first=Ben |last=Brantley |archivedate=2011-07-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110717043144/http://theater.nytimes.com/2011/02/04/theater/reviews/04three.html?pagewanted=2 |url=http://theater.nytimes.com/2011/02/04/theater/reviews/04three.html?pagewanted=2 |title=Russian Ennui, American Idiom |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2011-02-04 |work=The New York Times |page=2}}</ref>。

吉伦哈尔还在2012年的电影《[[永不退缩_(电影)|永不退缩]]》（{{lang|en|''Won't Back Down''}}）中饰演了一位参与父母触发而接管自己孩子所念学校的母亲，并在2013年的动作惊悚片《[[惊天危机|惊天危机]]》中诠释一位[[美国特勤局|美国特勤局]]探员<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Sneider |first1=Jeff | last2=Kroll |first2=Justin |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-12-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131203064509/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/maggie-gyllenhaal-joins-white-house-staff-1118055170/ |url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/maggie-gyllenhaal-joins-white-house-staff-1118055170/ | title=Maggie Gyllenhaal joins 'White House' staff | journal=Variety | date=2012-06-07}}</ref>。

=== 2021年后 ===
2021年，吉伦哈尔首次执导了心理剧《[[暗处的女儿|暗处的女儿]]》，同时担任制片人和编剧<ref>{{cite web|last=Debruge|first=Peter|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/reviews/the-lost-daughter-review-maggie-gyllenhaal-1235054843/|title=‘The Lost Daughter’ Review: ‘Unnatural Mother’ Olivia Colman Makes Amends in This Brilliant but Risky Thriller|website=Variety|date=2021-09-03|access-date=2021-11-12|archive-date=2021-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903211242/https://variety.com/2021/film/reviews/the-lost-daughter-review-maggie-gyllenhaal-1235054843/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该片受到好评<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lost_daughter|title=The Lost Daughter|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango Media]]|access-date=2021-11-12|archive-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114204648/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lost_daughter|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在[[第78屆威尼斯影展|第78屆威尼斯影展]]上首映，吉伦哈尔获得最佳剧本奖<ref name="vogue">{{cite news|last=Crescenti|first=Yelena|title=Festival del Cinema di Venezia 2021: tutti i vincitori|url=https://www.vogue.it/news/article/festival-cinema-venezia-2021-film-vincitori|date=2021-09-11|access-date=2021-09-12|website=[[Vogue_Italia|Vogue Italia]]|language=it|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122004141/https://www.vogue.it/news/article/festival-cinema-venezia-2021-film-vincitori|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[2021年哥譚獨立電影獎|2021年哥譚獨立電影獎]]三该片获得四个奖项，包括最佳影片和突破导演<ref name="indiewire">{{cite news|last1=Lattanzio|first1=Ryan|title=Gotham Awards: 'The Lost Daughter' Wins Top Prize — See the Full List of Winners|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/11/gotham-awards-2021-winners-list-1234682094/|access-date=2021-11-30|website=IndieWire|date=2021-11-30|archive-date=2021-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212190152/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/11/gotham-awards-2021-winners-list-1234682094/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[第79届金球奖|第79届金球奖]]上，吉伦哈尔获得最佳导演的提名。<ref name="golden_globes">{{cite web|last1=Moreau|first1=Jordan|last2=Lang|first2=Brent|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/golden-globes-nominations-list-nominees-1235129390/|title=Golden Globes 2022: The Complete Nominations List|website=Variety|date=2021-12-13|access-date=2021-12-14|archive-date=2021-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211213173919/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/golden-globes-nominations-list-nominees-1235129390/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

