吉伦哈尔从2002年起就开始与男演员彼得·萨斯加德交往<ref name="People - 2">{{cite news |first=Janet |last=Mock |url=http://www.people.com/people/maggie_gyllenhaal/biography/0,,20164968_10,00.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal Biography |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919024118/http://www.people.com/people/maggie_gyllenhaal/biography/0,,20164968_10,00.html |archivedate=2013-09-19 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-02-27 |work=People |page=2}}</ref>，后者是她弟弟杰克的好友<ref name="People - Bio" />。两人的婚约于2006年4月宣布<ref>{{cite news |author=Associated Press |deadurl=no |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2006-10-04-gyllenhaal-baby_x.htm?POE=LIFISVA |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal has a baby girl |date=2006-10-04 |work=USA Today |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-12-24 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131224172816/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2006-10-04-gyllenhaal-baby_x.htm?POE=LIFISVA}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1181971,00.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal, Peter Sarsgaard Expecting Baby |last=Hamm |first=Liza |coauthors=Mark Dagostino |date=2006-04-11 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130919012756/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1181971,00.html |deadurl=no |work=People |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-09-19}}</ref>，并于2009年5月2日在意大利[[布林迪西|布林迪西]]的一个小[[教堂|教堂]]成婚<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20276175,00.html |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal, Peter Sarsgaard Get Married |last=Wihlborg |first=Ulrica |date=2009-05-04 |work=People |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122215820/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20276175,00.html |archivedate=2014-01-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.denverpost.com/celebritybuzz/ci_12285554 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920153645/http://www.denverpost.com/celebritybuzz/ci_12285554 |title=People: Dolly Parton says "You starve or get fat" |last=Smith |first=Lori Spencer |date=2009-05-04 |work=The Denver Post |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-09-20}}</ref>。两人的长女雷蒙娜于2006年10月3日诞生<ref>{{cite news |first=Liza |last=Hamm |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1541965,00.html |title=Gyllenhaal, Sarsgaard Have a Girl |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919020143/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1541965,00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-09-19 |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2006-10-09 |work=People}}</ref>，二女儿格洛丽亚·雷于2012年4月19日出世<ref>{{cite news |first=Sarah |last=Michaud |archivedate=2014-02-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140207092829/http://celebritybabies.people.com/2012/04/30/maggie-gyllenhaal-peter-sarsgaard-welcome-daughter-gloria-ray/ |url=http://celebritybabies.people.com/2012/04/30/maggie-gyllenhaal-peter-sarsgaard-welcome-daughter-gloria-ray/ |title=Maggie Gyllenhaal and Peter Sarsgaard Welcome Daughter Gloria Ray |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2012-04-30 |work=People}}</ref>。一家人在纽约市的[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]生活<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140227091625/http://pagesix.com/2007/02/27/actress-seeks-safety-in-bklyn/ |url=http://pagesix.com/2007/02/27/actress-seeks-safety-in-bklyn/ |title=Actress seeks safety in B'klyn |last=Adams |first=Cindy |date=2007-02-27 |work=New York Post |accessdate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 政治立场 ==
吉伦哈尔积极参与[[政治|政治]]。她在2002年举行的第18届独立精神奖颁奖典礼上发言表示反对[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]，称这场战争的目的是“[[石油|石油]]和[[帝国主义|帝国主义]]”<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130918114339/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/03/24/movies/oscars-show-goes-on-but-mood-is-subdued-by-the-fighting-in-iraq.html |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/03/24/movies/oscars-show-goes-on-but-mood-is-subdued-by-the-fighting-in-iraq.html |title= Oscars Show Goes On, But Mood Is Subdued By the Fighting in Iraq |last=Madigan |first=Nick |date=2003-03-24 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.salon.com/2003/01/14/iraq_61/ |title=Wishing upon a star |last=Goldberg |first=Michelle |date=2003-01-13 |publisher=Salon.com |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227092457/http://www.salon.com/2003/01/14/iraq_61/ |archivedate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2005年，她针对[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]表示，应该就此为机遇，勇于对美国在世界上的作用提出一些严肃的质疑，无论是个人还是国家，对于自己是否有意或无意地促成这一事件扪心自问永远都是有意义的。这样的话引来了一些争议<ref name="bbc news">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4489365.stm |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120327193640/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4489365.stm |title=Actress Gyllenhaal in 9/11 outcry |accessdate=2014-02-27 |date=2005-04-27 |publisher=BBC |work=BBC News |archivedate=2012-03-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔还参与了[[罗伯特·格林沃德|罗伯特·格林沃德]]（{{lang|en|Robert Greenwald}}）发起的“艺术家团结起来不战而胜”（{{lang|en|Artists United to Win Without War}}）运动，其目标是推进[[进步主义|进步]]因素，为[[反对伊拉克战争|反对伊拉克战争]]代言<ref name="multiple" /><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222164736/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/03/20/us/threats-responses-california-approach-war-reveals-alienation-california.html |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/03/20/us/threats-responses-california-approach-war-reveals-alienation-california.html |title=Threats and Responses: California; Approach of War Reveals An Alienation in California|last=Murphy|first=Dean E. |date=2003-03-20 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>。她和弟弟杰克一起为[[摇滚投票|摇滚投票]]拍摄了一支[[广告|广告]]，并探访[[南加州大学|南加州大学]]校园，鼓励学生在[[2004年美国总统选举|2004年美国总统选举]]中踊跃投票<ref>{{cite news |first=Kara |last=Nichols |title=Celebrities rally voters |accessdate=2008-07-18 |date=2004-09-21 |work=Daily Trojan}}</ref>，她在这场选举中支持民主党候选人[[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://fpc.state.gov/fpc/37284.htm |title=Rock the Vote, the Youth Vote and the 2004 Presidential Election |last=Strell |first=Jay |date=2004-10-20 |work=United States Department of State Official Website |accessdate=2008-11-27 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20081127060750/http://fpc.state.gov/fpc/37284.htm |archivedate=2008-11-27 |deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131223055558/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485533/reese-kirsten-leo-attend-pro-vote-party.jhtml |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485533/reese-kirsten-leo-attend-pro-vote-party.jhtml |title=Celebs Go To The Post Office To Deliver Pro-Vote Message |last=Moss |first=Corey |date=2004-03-03 |work=MTV News |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>。[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年美国总统选举]]时，她支持的同样是民主党候选人[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/08/11/checking-out-the-parties-parties/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 |title=Checking Out the Parties’ Parties |last=Wayne |first=Leslie |date=2008-08-11 |work=The New York Times |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130518071552/http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/08/11/checking-out-the-parties-parties/ |archivedate=2013-05-18 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918183214/http://www.nme.com/news/kanye-west/38178 |url=http://www.nme.com/news/kanye-west/38178 |title=Kanye, Nerd, Wyclef for Democratic Convention |first=New York staff |date=2008-07-15 |work=NME |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref>。她还曾为[[美国公民自由联盟|美国公民自由联盟]]这个全家都强烈支持的组织进行宣传<ref name="farlanders">{{cite news |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/maggie-no-longer-looking-for-trouble-28441550.html |title=Maggie: No longer looking for trouble |date=2008-08-01 |work=The Belfast Telegraph |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127044952/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/maggie-no-longer-looking-for-trouble-28441550.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.aclu-sc.org/releases/view/100311 |title=ACLU To Honor Civil Liberties Champions At Annual Torch of Liberty Award Dinner Monday, May 19, 2003 |date=2003-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219233336/http://www.aclu-sc.org/releases/view/100311 |work=American Civil Liberties Union Official Website |accessdate=2012-02-19 |archivedate=2012-02-19 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

2013年6月，吉伦哈尔与多位艺人一起出现在一段支持[[切爾西·曼寧|切爾西·曼寧]]的视频中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2013/06/celebrity-bradley-manning-video-93041.html#ixzz2WgfpNmys |title=Celeb video  ‘I am Bradley Manning’ |first=Patrick Gavin |date=2013-06-19 |work=POLITICO.com |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110180932/http://www.politico.com/story/2013/06/celebrity-bradley-manning-video-93041.html#ixzz2WgfpNmys |archivedate=2014-01-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=UFFkcCh-pCc |title=I am Bradley Manning (full HD, 4:40) |author=[http://pardon.bradleymanning.org/ iam.bradleymanning.org] |coauthors=Maggie Gyllenhaal, Roger Waters, Oliver Stone, Daniel Ellsberg, Phil Donahue, Michael Ratner, Alice Walker, Tom Morello, Matt Taibbi, Peter Sarsgaard, Angela Davis, Moby, Molly Crabapple, Tim DeChristopher, LT Dan Choi, Bishop George Packard, Russell Brand, Allan Nairn, Chris Hedges, Wallace Shawn, Ahdaf Soueif... |date=2013-06-18 |publisher=YouTube |accessdate=2013-09-08 |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212020249/http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=UFFkcCh-pCc |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 慈善事业 ==
除了表演外，吉伦哈尔还是{{lang|en|[[Miu_Miu|Miu Miu]]}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/pop2it/2007/03/miu-miu-does-ru.html |title=Miu Miu: Does Rumer have it? |last=Snead |first=Elizabeth |date=2007-03-27 |work=Los Angeles Times |via=ZAP2it |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archivedate=2013-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705011735/http://blog.zap2it.com/pop2it/2007/03/miu-miu-does-ru.html |deadurl=no}}</ref>、[[锐步|锐步]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/2300-503023_162-4513556-3.html |title=Trendy and Green |date=2008-10-10 |publisher=CBS News |accessdate=2013-09-19 |archivedate=2013-09-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130919204100/http://www.cbsnews.com/2300-503023_162-4513556-3.html}}</ref>和[[大内密探_(内衣)|大内密探]]的代言[[模特儿|模特儿]]<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-12-22 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222101240/http://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2008/mar/09/fashion |deadurl=no |url= http://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2008/mar/09/fashion |title=How I get dressed |last=Wiseman |first=Eva |date=2008-03-09 |work=The Guardian |publisher=''guardian.co.uk'' |accessdate=2014-02-27 |location=London}}</ref>，并为[[希薇亞·普拉斯|希薇亞·普拉斯]]的[[小说|小说]]《[[钟罩_(小说)|钟罩]]》录制了第一本未删节版本的[[有声书|有声书]]<ref>{{cite journal |title=Audio Poetry: "Departure in New Affection and New Noise" |last=Hayes |first=Tim |date=2007-07-10 |work=The Missouri Review}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔还是非营利性组织[[证人_(人权组织)|证人]]的支持者，该组织利用视频和网络技术曝光侵犯人权的事件<ref>{{cite news |url=http://okmagazine.com/uncategorized/witnessing-maggie-gyllenhaal-goldie-hawn/ |deadurl=no |title=Witnessing Maggie Gyllenhaal, Goldie Hawn |last=Nome |first=Valerie |date=2007-11-18 |work=OK! |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140227101133/http://okmagazine.com/uncategorized/witnessing-maggie-gyllenhaal-goldie-hawn/ |archivedate=2014-02-27 |accessdate=2014-02-27}}</ref><ref name="wit organ">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917195223/http://www.witness.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=696&Itemid=249 |url=http://www.witness.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=696&Itemid=249 |title=Focus for Change Benefit |date=2007-11-07 |work=Witness Official Website |accessdate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-09-17}}</ref>。2007年11月，她与创始人[[彼得·蓋布瑞爾|彼得·蓋布瑞爾]]一起主持了一场公益晚宴<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110728154324/http://www.instyle.com/instyle/parties/party/0,,20159128_20364973,00.html |url=http://www.instyle.com/instyle/parties/party/0,,20159128_20364973,00.html |title=Peter Gabriel and Maggie Gyllenhaal |date=2007-11-18 |work=InStyle |accessdate=2011-07-28 |archivedate=2011-07-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918222137/http://www.hellomagazine.com/celebrities/2007/11/08/witness-sarandon-tim/ |url=http://www.hellomagazine.com/celebrities/2007/11/08/witness-sarandon-tim/ |title=Tim and Susan join fellow star campaigners at New York fundraiser |date=2007-11-08 |work=Hello! |accessdate=2014-02-27 |quote=Hosted by ''Stranger Than Fiction'' actress Maggie Gyllenhaal ... and musician Peter Gabriel, the event raised funds for human rights charity Witness. |archivedate=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。吉伦哈尔还帮助非营利性组织{{lang|en|TrickleUp.org}}筹款，该组织旨在帮助贫困人士创立[[微型企业|微型企业]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.instyle.com/instyle/package/holidaytrends/photos/0,,20063741_20153720_20374556,00.html |title=Ten Thousand Things Charm Necklace |date=2007-12 |work=InStyle |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-12-22 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222165936/http://www.instyle.com/instyle/package/holidaytrends/photos/0,,20063741_20153720_20374556,00.html |deadurl=no}}</ref>。作为募捐人之一，她帮助设计和宣传了一款售价100美元的项链，所有销售收益都将进入慈善机构<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.seventeen.com/cosmogirl/trickle-up-charity-necklace-120607 |title=Trickle Up's Charity Necklace |date=2007-12-06 |work=Seventeen |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2012-03-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308100407/http://www.seventeen.com/cosmogirl/trickle-up-charity-necklace-120607 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2008年10月，她在洛杉矶主持了一场由{{lang|en|[[Gen_Art|Gen Art]]}}和{{lang|en|SoyJoy}}推出，名为“天然时尚”（{{lang|en|"Fashionably Natural"}}）的时装秀活动<ref name="eco" /><ref name="friendly" />，其中主要展出了四位崭露头角设计师的作品，完全由天然或环保的面料和材料制作<ref name="eco">{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/features/la-ig-genart5-2008oct05,0,4400002.story |title=Gen Art showcases the faces of fashion's future |last=Tschorn |first=Adam |date=2008-10-05 |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archivedate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131222052750/http://www.latimes.com/features/la-ig-genart5-2008oct05,0,4400002.story}}</ref><ref name="friendly">{{cite news |url=http://www.soyjoy.com/drawPDF.aspx?pdf=GENARTSOYJOYPRESENTFASHIONABLYNATURAL20090121110003|title=Gen Art and SoyJoy Present ''Fashionably Natural'' |accessdate=2010-02-25 |date=2008-09-25 |work=SoyJoy Official Website |format=Press release |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100225110256/http://www.soyjoy.com/drawPDF.aspx?pdf=GENARTSOYJOYPRESENTFASHIONABLYNATURAL20090121110003 |archivedate=2010-02-25}}</ref>。

